<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV19">
<l>puḷḷatāki vētanāṉku mōtiṉāya taṉṟiyum</l>
<l>puḷḷiṉvāypi ḷantupuṭko ṭippiṭitta piṉṉarum</l>
<l>puḷḷaiyūrti yātalāla teṉkolmiṉko ṇēmiyāy</l>
<l>puḷḷiṉmeyppa kaikkaṭaṟki ṭattalkāta littatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Becoming a [haṃsa] bird, You uttered the four Vedas.</l>
<l>Other than that, splitting the bird’s beak and hoisting the [bird] banner,</l>
<l>You ride the bird, O you with a flashing discus!</l>
<l>Why, then, do you desire to lie down on the ocean,</l>
<l rend="indent">upon the true enemy of the bird?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
